    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082688_5_721-745",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "721-745",
      "markText": "那里草地上有一所亚洲学校的学生在做奇怪缓慢的动作",
      "totalCount": 600,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300082688&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=721&rangeEnd=745",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dbe32a40813ab86ccg018ae7?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=721&rangeEnd=745"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082688_12_1614-1657",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1614-1657",
      "markText": "没有人有权利去装模作样重现一个已不在世的人的生平。没有人有权利凭一个木偶去创作一个人。",
      "totalCount": 528,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300082688&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1614&rangeEnd=1657",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dbe32a40813ab86ccg018ae7?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1614&rangeEnd=1657"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082688_5_545-637",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "545-637",
      "markText": "他事前知道自己没有力量心甘情愿变成长蛇阵的一部分；他观察这些人，观察他们因厌烦而麻痹的面孔，想象展厅内那些展品全被他们的身体与闲聊遮蔽，以至一分钟后他别转身子，走上横穿公园的一条小路。",
      "totalCount": 527,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300082688&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=545&rangeEnd=637",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dbe32a40813ab86ccg018ae7?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=545&rangeEnd=637"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082688_31_1169-1227",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "1169-1227",
      "markText": "我们很久以来就明白世界是不可能推翻的，不可能改造的，也是不可能阻挡其不幸的进展的。只有一种可能的抵挡：不必认真对待。",
      "totalCount": 506,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300082688&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1169&rangeEnd=1227",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dbe32a40813ab86ccg018ae7?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1169&rangeEnd=1227"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082688_15_1937-2026",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "1937-2026",
      "markText": "一阵沉默后，拉蒙说：“阿兰，你说得合情合理。我死后，要每十年醒来一次，来证实加里宁格勒是否还是加里宁格勒。如果依然不变，我跟人类还是意气相投的，跟其重归于好后再回到我的坟墓里去。",
      "totalCount": 462,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300082688&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1937&rangeEnd=2026",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dbe32a40813ab86ccg018ae7?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1937&rangeEnd=2026"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082688_18_1032-1093",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "1032-1093",
      "markText": "但是怎么啦？她忘了自己的决心吗？如果试图救她于不死的人不再活着，她为什么不把自己溺死呢？为什么最后自由了她又不想去死了呢？",
      "totalCount": 442,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300082688&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1032&rangeEnd=1093",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/dbe32a40813ab86ccg018ae7?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1032&rangeEnd=1093"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300082688_5_949-987",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "949-987",
      "markText": "这份冷淡让拉蒙感受到平静与安慰。渐渐地，在他脸上露出长时间几乎是幸福的微笑。",
